data.description: If you're looking for a quiet place to call home that's tucked within the trees, this adorable property that is situated on 5.3 acres in Palmyra Township is waiting for you! Completely remodeled in 2017, this 3 bedroom and 2 full bathroom home features an open concept floor plan with a large kitchen, tons of natural light, and the perfect amount of privacy outside. The main living area has beautiful bamboo floors that run throughout the kitchen, living room, dining room, and hallway. On the lower level, you will find a cozy family room, complete with a wood burning stove, and a beautifully updated second full bathroom. The lower level also has access to the 2 car attached garage. Updates include HVAC (2017), hot water tank (2017), full kitchen remodel with granite counter tops (2017), full bathroom remodels (2017), all kitchen appliances (2017), septic (2020), rain soft water system (2021), and Roof (2022).
